metadata.name: Floral Lead
metadata.description:
Three knights fell in love with a beautiful girl who lived in a village.  
Unable to choose just one, she asked Flora, the goddess of flowers, to change her into the form of a flower.  
  
How lovely she looked in bloom, swaying in the spring breeze.  
The girl in my memory hid in the shadow of the flower and did not come back even after a while.  
...  
Inspired by the legend of the Dutch tulip
